  "detailed_description": "A great tournament is organized in the brand new gameroom : Runner Party!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874950/extras/6ff9bed8c30bd2f609bac14ec7268552.poster.avif?t=1683021449\" width=628 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874950/extras/6ff9bed8c30bd2f609bac14ec7268552.webm?t=1683021449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874950/extras/6ff9bed8c30bd2f609bac14ec7268552.mp4?t=1683021449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Runner Party is a local and multiplayer Steam Remote play with diverse mechanics. <br><br>A competitive Multiplayer game up to 4 players<br><br>In a 80’s and 90’s universe, you can participate in fun races filled with platforms and filled with obstacles. <br><br>You will have many items to separate yourself from your opponents and win the race ! Get out of the screen and you will be eliminated ! <br><br>Be the most responsive to win the race by winning 3 rounds !<br><br>Become a legend ! 3 ! 2 ! 1 ! Go !<br><br>A competitive Multiplayer game up to 4 players<br><br><br>Runner Party is in early access.<br>The game will evolve quickly and offer later<br><br>- 1 character editor (win and collect cards to get new skins ! Customize your character ! )<br><br>- Additional levels<br>- an AI to play alone<br>- Servers to play online<br>- A complete matchmaking system as well as many leagues<br><br>Join us on discord !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874950/extras/e2357caf8c6b97a727df97cea6f6bfd1.poster.avif?t=1683021449\" width=628 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874950/extras/e2357caf8c6b97a727df97cea6f6bfd1.webm?t=1683021449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874950/extras/e2357caf8c6b97a727df97cea6f6bfd1.mp4?t=1683021449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "A great tournament is organized in the brand new gameroom : Runner Party!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874950/extras/6ff9bed8c30bd2f609bac14ec7268552.poster.avif?t=1683021449\" width=628 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874950/extras/6ff9bed8c30bd2f609bac14ec7268552.webm?t=1683021449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874950/extras/6ff9bed8c30bd2f609bac14ec7268552.mp4?t=1683021449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Runner Party is a local and multiplayer Steam Remote play with diverse mechanics. <br><br>A competitive Multiplayer game up to 4 players<br><br>In a 80’s and 90’s universe, you can participate in fun races filled with platforms and filled with obstacles. <br><br>You will have many items to separate yourself from your opponents and win the race ! Get out of the screen and you will be eliminated ! <br><br>Be the most responsive to win the race by winning 3 rounds !<br><br>Become a legend ! 3 ! 2 ! 1 ! Go !<br><br>A competitive Multiplayer game up to 4 players<br><br><br>Runner Party is in early access.<br>The game will evolve quickly and offer later<br><br>- 1 character editor (win and collect cards to get new skins ! Customize your character ! )<br><br>- Additional levels<br>- an AI to play alone<br>- Servers to play online<br>- A complete matchmaking system as well as many leagues<br><br>Join us on discord !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874950/extras/e2357caf8c6b97a727df97cea6f6bfd1.poster.avif?t=1683021449\" width=628 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/18749